{
  "stem": "11175.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they took care of him quite a few days, the first few days after the liquidation from there-- and they take care.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Then we take the child out from there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And she said, the woman-- wife, at that time, I'm going to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I'm going to take-- as a Polish woman, I will try to go to [NON-ENGLISH] We heard that in [NON-ENGLISH], they have some more freedom.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They live better.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they can go into work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she said-- we-- she hired somebody, we hired-- we hired a woman, a Polish woman.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She should keep her company, and go in with her to [NON-ENGLISH], she should be in [NON-ENGLISH], she should live there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And meanwhile, this woman what we hired, she was not interested in her life, either on that child's life-- she was more interesting to see to go into that house where she lived and take out from there everything.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said, you stay here, and I'm going to-- and a day later, she didn't-- they were hiding, and they couldn't get out because they need something to do.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Near Otwock was a camp, a working camp, which they had that organized before the-- the liquidation from that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were working there on that camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When the-- my wife's father said, look, I have some friends that maybe we going to go to that camp, maybe they will be able to get into that camp and stay there until that's the time to regulate a little bit.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remained in ghetto with some other boys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were hiding ourselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were-- you know, if there were Germans, we know-- we were young men, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I could run around.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
